---
const year = 2026;
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<footer class="main-footer">
    <div class="footer-container">
        <div class="footer-grid">
    <div class="footer-info">
        <a href={base} class="footer-logo-link">
            <img
                src={base + "/MPZ_logo_horiz_fullcolor_negative.svg"}
                alt="Marta Zola Logo"
                class="footer-logo-img"
            />
        </a>
        <p class="footer-tagline">Naturopatia integrata per il benessere femminile</p>
        <p class="footer-vat">P.IVA 14524810968</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-newsletter">
        <h4 class="footer-title">Newsletter</h4>
        <p>Iscriviti a "Semi", la mia newsletter con consigli, riflessioni e pillole di Naturopatia.</p>
        <a href={base + "/newsletter"} class="footer-btn-newsletter">
            <span>Iscriviti ora</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"/></svg>
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-nav">
        <h4 class="footer-title">Menu</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><a href={base + "/chi-sono"}>Chi Sono</a></li>
            <li><a href={base + "/servizi"}>Servizi</a></li>
            <li><a href={base + "/contatti"}>Contatti</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-legal">
        <h4 class="footer-title">Social & Legal</h4>
        <div class="footer-social">
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/marta_zola_naturopata/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="20" height="20" x="2" y="2" rx="5" ry="5"></rect><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"></path><line x1="17.5" x2="17.51" y1="6.5" y2="6.5"></line></svg>
                <span>Instagram</span>
            </a>
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="/cookie-policy">Cookie Policy</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

        <div class="footer-bottom">
            <p class="legal-disclaimer">Le pratiche proposte hanno finalità di accompagnamento e benessere e non sostituiscono diagnosi, terapie o il rapporto con il medico o altri professionisti della salute.<br/>
                In caso di necessità, rivolgiti sempre a un professionista sanitario qualificato.</p>
            <p>&copy; {year} Marta Zola. Tutti i diritti riservati.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>

<style>
    .main-footer {
        background-color: var(--accent-4);
        color: var(--bg-light);
        padding: 5rem 1.5rem 2rem;
        font-family: var(--font-body);
    }

    .footer-container {
        max-width: var(--container-width);
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .footer-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 4fr 3fr 1fr 2fr; /* Proporzioni bilanciate */
        gap: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .footer-logo-link {
        display: inline-block;
    }

    .footer-logo-img {
        height: 45px; /* Regola l'altezza desiderata */
        width: auto;
        display: block;
    }

    .footer-tagline {
        font-size: .9rem;
        margin-top:0.3rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .footer-vat {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .footer-title {
        font-family: var(--font-headings);
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--brand-gold);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1rem;
    }

    .footer-grid ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .footer-grid ul li {
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .footer-grid ul li a {
        color: var(--bg-light);
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .footer-grid ul li a:hover {
        color: var(--brand-gold);
        opacity: 1;
    }

    /* Stile del testo e del bottone Newsletter */
.footer-newsletter p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
}

.footer-btn-newsletter {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    background-color: transparent;
    color: var(--brand-gold);
    border: 1px solid var(--brand-gold);
    padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: var(--font-headings);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border-radius: 4px;
}

.footer-btn-newsletter:hover {
    background-color: var(--brand-gold);
    color: var(--accent-4); /* Il colore scuro del tuo footer */
}

.footer-btn-newsletter svg {
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.footer-btn-newsletter:hover svg {
    transform: translateX(4px);
}

    .footer-social {
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .footer-social a {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        color: var(--bg-light);
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .footer-social a:hover {
        color: var(--brand-gold);
        opacity: 1;
    }

    .social-icon {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
    }

    .footer-bottom {
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        padding-top: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        opacity: 0.6;
    }

    .legal-disclaimer{
        font-size:12px;
    }


    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .footer-grid {
        /* Crea due colonne di larghezza uguale */
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; 
        gap: 3rem;
    }

    .footer-info {
        /* Rimuoviamo lo span 2 per farlo stare in una colonna sola */
        grid-column: span 1; 
        text-align: left; /* Opzionale: allinea a sinistra per coerenza */
    }

    /* Le altre colonne (Newsletter, Menu, Legal) si posizioneranno 
       automaticamente seguendo il flusso della griglia:
       Riga 1: Info | Newsletter
       Riga 2: Menu | Legal 
    */

    .footer-nav,
    .footer-legal,
    .footer-newsletter {
        text-align: left; /* Allineamento coerente su tablet */
    }

    .footer-social a {
        justify-content: flex-start; /* Allinea l'icona social a sinistra */
    }
}

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
    /* 1. Forza la griglia a diventare una colonna singola */
    .footer-grid {
        display: flex !important;
        flex-direction: column !important;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; 
        gap: 3rem;
        text-align: center;
        width: 100%;
    }

    /* 2. Centra i blocchi interni */
    .footer-info, 
    .footer-newsletter, 
    .footer-nav, 
    .footer-legal {
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center; /* Centra orizzontalmente i figli */
    }

    /* 3. Sistema i testi e i titoli */
    .footer-title {
        text-align: center;
        width: 100%;
    }

    /* 4. Rimuovi eventuali float residui di MailerLite che spostano le cose */
    .ml-form-embedWrapper, .ml-form-embedContainer {
        float: none !important;
        margin: 0 auto !important;
        width: 100% !important;
    }

    /* 5. Sistema la lista dei link del menu */
    .footer-nav ul, 
    .footer-legal ul {
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .footer-social a {
        justify-content: center;
    }
}
</style>